---
title: Sticky Mango Chicken Breast Noodles with Stir-Fried Veg
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sticky Mango Chicken Breast  Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W26_UK_V22127-3_Main_low-905eff1e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/662a2ae676c8ff773e073456-en-GB.pdf
